<h1>Who We Are — BrightMark Digital Agency</h1>

<p>Founded in 2019, BrightMark Digital Agency has helped over 200 small and medium businesses achieve measurable online growth. Our team of SEO specialists, ad managers, and content creators is passionate about delivering real results.</p>

<h2>Our Mission</h2>
<p>To make digital marketing accessible and profitable for every business.</p>

<h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
<p>Ravi Sharma - SEO Head | Priya Singh - PPC Manager | Amit Verma - Content Lead</p>

<h2>Our Core Values</h2>
<p>Transparency | Data-Driven | Client-First</p>

